                    <span>What can I say?  This book is probably the closest Chinese book involving the art of parallel-argumentation that a person will ever get out of a Chinese book.  
<br />
<br />I love this book.  Plus, Lau really adds desert by his five highly detailed appendixes.  Way to go Lau!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">"To try to achieve anything is like digging a well. "</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
